Uh?

18
00:00:57,150 --> 00:01:00,275
Liberation: Wind Prison.

19
00:01:04,567 --> 00:01:05,650
[NAOFUMI]
Melty!

20
00:01:06,567 --> 00:01:09,525
[gasps] What's happening to me?

21
00:01:10,650 --> 00:01:11,608
[MELTY yelps]

22
00:01:13,442 --> 00:01:16,525
She's my friend.
What are you doing to her?!

23
00:01:16,608 --> 00:01:18,275
I'm sorry, but I'm
going to have to

24
