53
00:02:44,233 --> 00:02:46,192
<i>Just fight it out</i>

54
00:02:47,317 --> 00:02:49,275
<i>Just fight it out</i>

55
00:02:53,108 --> 00:02:54,567
Your hostage?

56
00:02:54,650 --> 00:02:56,192
Why are you doing this?

57
00:02:56,275 --> 00:02:59,358
[FITORIA] I need your
promise, Shield Hero.

58
00:02:59,442 --> 00:03:02,067
Promise me you'll reconcile
with the others.

59
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:04,858
You're a meanie! You let Mel go!

60
00:03:04,942 --> 00:03:06,108
[NAOFUMI]
What if I don't?

61
00:03:06,192 --> 00:03:08,442
Are you threatening
to hurt the princess?

62
00:03:08,525 --> 00:03:10,483
[MELTY gasps]

63
00:03:10,567 --> 00:03:12,692
I told you, that's
never gonna happen.

64
00:03:12,775 --> 00:03:16,317
[FITORIA] Nevertheless,
I must ask you to reconsider.

65
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:19,358
Why are you so obsessed with
making us work together anyway?

66
00:03:19,442 --> 00:03:21,275
[FITORIA] Because I had
made a promise of my own

67
00:03:21,358 --> 00:03:24,317
a long time ago,
to the hero who raised me.

68
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:27,775
And because, if this
world is going to survive,

69
00:03:27,858 --> 00:03:31,692
the Cardinal Heroes must work
together to fight off the Waves.

70
00:03:31,775 --> 00:03:33,067
I beg you.

71
00:03:33,150 --> 00:03:35,358
No matter how many
times you ask,

72
00:03:35,442 --> 00:03:38,025
I'm not gonna make
nice with those idiots.

73
00:03:38,108 --> 00:03:39,525
Then there's no choice.

74
00:03:39,608 --> 00:03:42,525
If you won't work together,
new heroes will be summoned.

75
00:03:42,608 --> 00:03:45,108
Which means all four of
the heroes we have now

76
00:03:45,192 --> 00:03:47,442
must be removed.

77
00:03:47,525 --> 00:03:48,900
[ALL gasp]

78
00:03:48,983 --> 00:03:50,025
You'd kill all of us

79
00:03:50,108 --> 00:03:51,858
just because we don't
like each other?

80
00:03:51,942 --> 00:03:54,275
[FITORIA] That is what's
best for the world.

81
00:03:55,317 --> 00:03:56,983
[NAOFUMI] Yeah...
She wouldn't have any trouble

82
00:03:57,067 --> 00:03:58,733
pulling it off, either.

83
00:03:59,775 --> 00:04:02,733
But if you all reconcile,
I won't have to.

84
00:04:02,817 --> 00:04:04,733
[NAOFUMI grunts]

85
00:04:04,817 --> 00:04:09,067
I understand...
but I still can't do it.

86
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:12,483
And taking Melty hostage
doesn't change anything.

87
00:04:12,567 --> 00:04:14,858
If you want to kill me,
knock yourself out.

88
00:04:15,942 --> 00:04:16,775
[NAOFUMI]
Bring it.

89
00:04:16,858 --> 00:04:18,858
--Naofumi!
--Master Naofumi!

90
00:04:18,942 --> 00:04:22,025
[NAOFUMI] But I promise I'm not
goin' down without a fight!

91
00:04:23,817 --> 00:04:24,942
No need.

92
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:28,733
[NAOFUMI grunts]

93
00:04:28,817 --> 00:04:30,483
[NAOFUMI gasps]
Not again!

94
00:04:30,567 --> 00:04:33,233
[FITORIA] I understand
how you feel, Shield Hero.

95
00:04:33,317 --> 00:04:34,900
You what?

96
00:04:34,983 --> 00:04:36,275
I'll give you a chance.

97
00:04:36,358 --> 00:04:38,192
If you can prove to me
that you and your party

98
00:04:38,275 --> 00:04:40,067
can defeat the
Waves of Catastrophe

99
00:04:40,150 --> 00:04:41,858
without assistance
from the other heroes,

100
00:04:41,942 --> 00:04:43,275
I'll let you live.

101
00:04:43,358 --> 00:04:44,650
How do we do that?

102
00:04:44,733 --> 00:04:46,650
That's generous of you.

103
00:04:46,733 --> 00:04:48,650
So what? You want us to
fight you right here?

104
00:04:48,733 --> 00:04:51,400
Actually, I'm already familiar
with your capabilities,

105
00:04:51,483 --> 00:04:52,775
Shield Hero.

106
00:04:54,817 --> 00:04:57,025
Filo must fight me alone.

107
00:04:57,108 --> 00:04:57,942
--[NAOFUMI grunts]
--[FILO gasps]

108
00:04:58,025 --> 00:04:59,483
Why me?

109
00:04:59,567 --> 00:05:01,942
If you can show me that you
are, in fact, strong enough,

110
00:05:02,025 --> 00:05:03,942
I will release Melty.

111
00:05:04,025 --> 00:05:06,358
And I also won't do
anything to harm the heroes

112
00:05:06,442 --> 00:05:07,942
for the time being, either.

113
00:05:08,025 --> 00:05:09,817
They'll live for now.

114
00:05:11,317 --> 00:05:13,442
I don't really understand
everything you're saying,

115
00:05:13,525 --> 00:05:15,567
but if I beat you,
Master won't be killed,

116
00:05:15,650 --> 00:05:17,942
and you'll let
Mel go, too, right?

117
00:05:18,025 --> 00:05:18,900
[NAOFUMI]
Wait, hang on a second--

118
00:05:18,983 --> 00:05:20,983
Then you've got yourself a duel.

119
00:05:21,067 --> 00:05:23,650
I'm going to fight you
in my human form, Filo.

120
00:05:23,733 --> 00:05:27,233
I ask that you maintain yours
until it's over, as well.

121
00:05:28,483 --> 00:05:29,483
No problem!

122
00:05:29,567 --> 00:05:31,483
Filo, I told you to wait!

123
00:05:32,942 --> 00:05:34,192
Let's begin.

124
00:05:46,108 --> 00:05:47,858
I'm coming for you!

125
00:05:47,942 --> 00:05:49,275
Go right ahead.

126
00:05:53,442 --> 00:05:55,650
[FILO yells]

127
00:05:57,525 --> 00:05:58,650
Too slow.

128
00:05:58,733 --> 00:06:01,233
[FILO gasps, yells]

129
00:06:04,983 --> 00:06:06,233
[FILO]
Huh?

130
00:06:06,317 --> 00:06:07,608
Filo! Watch out!

131
00:06:08,775 --> 00:06:10,442
[gasps]

132
00:06:12,650 --> 00:06:14,358
[gasps] Filo!

133
00:06:16,317 --> 00:06:18,650
[FILO groans]

134
00:06:20,567 --> 00:06:22,025
[NAOFUMI]
This doesn't make sense.

135
00:06:22,108 --> 00:06:25,650
Why did Fitoria want to fight
Filo and not Raphtalia?

136
00:06:25,733 --> 00:06:29,608
And why would she want both of
them to fight in human form?

137
00:06:29,692 --> 00:06:30,900
Damn it.

138
00:06:30,983 --> 00:06:34,150
Filo! You can't just keep
charging in like that!

139
00:06:34,233 --> 00:06:36,650
You've gotta use your head!

140
00:06:36,733 --> 00:06:38,192
I'll try, Master.

141
00:06:38,275 --> 00:06:41,358
[NAOFUMI] And regenerate your
clothes as soon as possible!

142
00:06:41,442 --> 00:06:44,442
Put some mana into it so you
can increase your defense!

143
00:06:46,192 --> 00:06:48,608
[grunts] Whatever you say!

144
00:06:49,733 --> 00:06:52,483
[FILO] As source of
thy power, I order thee.

145
00:06:52,567 --> 00:06:54,358
Decipher the laws of nature

146
00:06:54,442 --> 00:06:57,817
and use a giant whirlwind
to blow my target away!

147
00:06:58,858 --> 00:07:01,775
Go, Zweit Tornado!

148
00:07:02,942 --> 00:07:05,858
I'm afraid that won't be
enough to win this fight.

149
00:07:05,942 --> 00:07:08,275
Anti-Zweit Tornado!

150
00:07:10,525 --> 00:07:11,525
[gasps, grunts]

151
00:07:11,608 --> 00:07:14,067
Look out! She's using
jamming magic!

152
00:07:15,317 --> 00:07:17,275
--[FILO gasps]
--You're wide open.

153
00:07:17,358 --> 00:07:18,483
[FILO groans]

154
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:24,525
[FILO groaning]

155
00:07:24,608 --> 00:07:27,775
She's not even getting a chance
to regenerate her clothes.

156
00:07:32,692 --> 00:07:34,233
--[NAOFUMI] Melty.
--[MELTY gasps]

157
00:07:34,317 --> 00:07:36,858
If this keeps up,
Filo's in trouble.

158
00:07:36,942 --> 00:07:40,192
I'm gonna use my shield to break
you out of this cage instead.

159
00:07:43,983 --> 00:07:46,192
[NAOFUMI grunts, groans]

160
00:07:47,442 --> 00:07:49,483
--Naofumi!
--Master Naofumi!

161
00:07:49,567 --> 00:07:51,025
[groans]

162
00:07:52,483 --> 00:07:54,567
[NAOFUMI] The shield's defense
is like nothing to her!

163
00:07:54,650 --> 00:07:55,983
Master, you're hurt!

164
00:07:56,067 --> 00:07:57,983
[FITORIA]
Eyes on your opponent.

165
00:07:58,067 --> 00:07:59,025
[FILO groans]

166
00:08:00,067 --> 00:08:03,192
That attack was necessary to
prevent him from cheating.

167
00:08:03,275 --> 00:08:04,650
He deserved it.

168
00:08:04,733 --> 00:08:05,942
[FILO pants]

169
00:08:06,025 --> 00:08:08,192
[FITORIA] Do you know
why he attempted that?

170
00:08:08,275 --> 00:08:10,733
Because you're weak, Filo.

171
00:08:10,817 --> 00:08:12,567
[FILO gasps]

172
00:08:12,650 --> 00:08:15,525
[FITORIA] Can you tell me
what you are fighting for?

173
00:08:15,608 --> 00:08:18,400
[FILO] I would've
thought that was obvious.

174
00:08:18,483 --> 00:08:20,775
I'm fighting for my master!

175
00:08:20,858 --> 00:08:22,442
You couldn't beat
the dragon last night

176
00:08:22,525 --> 00:08:24,317
and you can't beat me now.

177
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:27,567
How do you expect to be of
any use to the Shield Hero?

178
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:29,692
[FILO growls]
I'm won't lose to you!

179
00:08:29,775 --> 00:08:32,858
I'll become strong for
Master and I'll beat you!

180
00:08:32,942 --> 00:08:35,317
Not with willpower
as shallow as yours!

181
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,400
[FILO groans]

182
00:08:43,108 --> 00:08:44,150
[NAOFUMI groans]

183
00:08:44,233 --> 00:08:46,442
Oh, Master Naofumi.
Are you all right?

184
00:08:46,525 --> 00:08:48,233
Yeah, I think I'm okay.

185
00:08:48,317 --> 00:08:50,983
[FILO] I'm not letting
Master get hurt ever again!

186
00:08:51,067 --> 00:08:52,275
[BOTH gasp]

187
00:08:52,358 --> 00:08:54,983
[FILO] I'm... I'm going
to get so much stronger

188
00:08:55,067 --> 00:08:57,817
than I've ever been before!

189
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:59,692
Will you?

190
00:08:59,775 --> 00:09:01,692
[inhales]

191
00:09:06,192 --> 00:09:07,733
What's she doing?

192
00:09:07,817 --> 00:09:11,233
She's absorbing all the
mana particles in the air.

193
00:09:11,317 --> 00:09:13,775
I didn't think that
was even possible!

194
00:09:13,858 --> 00:09:15,400
[FILO gasps]

195
00:09:15,483 --> 00:09:16,608
[NAOFUMI]
Filo!

196
00:09:17,650 --> 00:09:19,275
[FILO]
Master...

197
00:09:19,358 --> 00:09:21,150
Stop worrying about me.

198
00:09:21,233 --> 00:09:22,650
I'll be fine, okay?

199
00:09:22,733 --> 00:09:25,025
Just stay calm and
watch her attacks!

200
00:09:25,108 --> 00:09:27,400
You can do this! I know it!

201
00:09:27,483 --> 00:09:29,317
[gasps]

202
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,483
I know that you can do this.

203
00:09:33,067 --> 00:09:34,150
[FILO]
Yeah!

204
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:41,567
You're too slow.

205
00:09:41,650 --> 00:09:44,150
[FILO]
Maybe, but I'll still beat you!

206
00:09:46,442 --> 00:09:47,358
[FILO grunts]

207
00:09:47,442 --> 00:09:52,608
Spiral Strike!

208
00:09:57,858 --> 00:10:01,275
[yells]

209
00:10:01,358 --> 00:10:02,692
Oh, Filo!

210
00:10:02,775 --> 00:10:07,275
[yelling]

211
00:10:18,358 --> 00:10:19,942
That was incredible!

212
00:10:20,025 --> 00:10:22,442
Wow. Can you believe
she just did that?

213
00:10:22,525 --> 00:10:24,025
She did it.

214
00:10:24,108 --> 00:10:27,400
[FILO groaning]

215
00:10:27,483 --> 00:10:32,483
I won't lose... [pants]

216
00:10:32,567 --> 00:10:36,608
I won't... [pants]

217
00:10:36,692 --> 00:10:38,817
I'll grow stronger...

218
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:42,067
I have to... for Master.

219
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:44,442
I have to be strong enough...

220
00:10:44,525 --> 00:10:48,233
...to protect Mel...
and Raphtalia...

221
00:10:48,317 --> 00:10:52,567
I have to be strong enough...
to protect everyone...!

222
00:10:54,483 --> 00:10:55,483
[FITORIA]
Good.

223
00:10:56,525 --> 00:10:58,358
[FILO]
That way...

224
00:10:58,442 --> 00:11:00,108
...I won't lose...

225
00:11:00,192 --> 00:11:01,733
...ever again.

226
00:11:03,358 --> 00:11:05,817
[FITORIA]
That's enough now, Filo.

227
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:08,150
I believe you've beaten me.

228
00:11:08,233 --> 00:11:09,983
[FILO]
Huh?

229
00:11:10,067 --> 00:11:12,275
[FITORIA] And you've
earned Melty's freedom.

230
00:11:12,358 --> 00:11:14,650
You're strong enough after all.

231
00:11:14,733 --> 00:11:16,525
--[MELTY] Oh, Filo!
--[FILO gasps]

232
00:11:16,608 --> 00:11:20,192
[MELTY whimpers, sobs]

233
00:11:20,275 --> 00:11:22,067
[FILO gasps]

234
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,942
Mel, I... did it...!

235
00:11:24,025 --> 00:11:26,400
--[footsteps]
--[gasps]

236
00:11:26,483 --> 00:11:28,567
Did you see that, Master?

237
00:11:28,650 --> 00:11:29,442
I won.

238
00:11:29,525 --> 00:11:31,025
Did you see?

239
00:11:31,108 --> 00:11:32,400
Sure did.

240
00:11:32,483 --> 00:11:34,400
You were amazing, Filo.

241
00:11:34,483 --> 00:11:36,025
[FILO giggles]

242
00:11:43,983 --> 00:11:47,108
[FITORIA sighs] I'm quite
glad you passed the trial.

243
00:11:47,192 --> 00:11:48,317
Huh?

244
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:49,317
Couldn't tell?

245
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,192
Fitoria was testing you.

246
00:11:51,275 --> 00:11:52,900
[FILO gasps]

247
00:11:52,983 --> 00:11:55,067
[FITORIA]
Yes. But it was a serious test,

248
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:57,650
because if you hadn't passed it,
you would have died.

249
00:11:57,733 --> 00:11:59,525
And the Shield Hero
would have died as well.

250
00:11:59,608 --> 00:12:01,233
--[NAOFUMI grunts]
--Huh?

251
00:12:01,317 --> 00:12:02,567
[NAOFUMI, RAPHTALIA gasp]

252
00:12:04,192 --> 00:12:05,858
[FILO]
Ooh, what's that?

253
00:12:05,942 --> 00:12:06,983
[FITORIA]
Your reward.

254
00:12:07,067 --> 00:12:10,025
To honor you for
overcoming my trial.

255
00:12:10,108 --> 00:12:11,775
Please lower your head.

256
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:17,567
[filolials squawk]

257
00:12:17,650 --> 00:12:22,483
[FITORIA] Filo, I am delighted
to appoint you as my successor.

258
00:12:22,567 --> 00:12:24,108
Successor?

259
00:12:25,608 --> 00:12:27,275
Are you saying that
Filo's going to become

260
00:12:27,358 --> 00:12:29,358
the next queen of the filolials?

261
00:12:29,442 --> 00:12:30,817
[MELTY]
Congratulations, Filo!

262
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:32,358
Huh?

263
00:12:35,317 --> 00:12:37,567
Uh--wha...?

264
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:40,358
I guess that's the symbol
of filolial royalty?

265
00:12:40,442 --> 00:12:42,442
[NAOFUMI]
Their crown is a cowlick?!

266
00:12:42,525 --> 00:12:44,067
Oh, it's adorable!

267
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:46,942
[FILO gasps] Get this
weird thing off my head!

268
00:12:47,025 --> 00:12:49,775
[FILO whines, grunts]

269
00:12:49,858 --> 00:12:50,692
[FILO giggles]

270
00:12:51,733 --> 00:12:52,567
--[FILO gasps]
--[MELTY squeals]

271
00:12:52,650 --> 00:12:53,942
Look, it grew back!

272
00:12:54,025 --> 00:12:55,442
[FILO]
Why?!

273
00:12:55,525 --> 00:12:57,942
And it always will, so I'd
get used to it if I were you.

274
00:12:58,025 --> 00:13:00,025
And as you grow older
and gain strength,

275
00:13:00,108 --> 00:13:01,400
you'll have more of them.

276
00:13:01,483 --> 00:13:03,608
[FILO] Does that mean
I'm gonna look like you?

277
00:13:03,692 --> 00:13:06,317
--[FILO groans]
--[MELTY squeals]

278
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:08,400
[NAOFUMI]
Her stats have increased.

279
00:13:08,483 --> 00:13:09,942
Does that cowlick
give her bonuses

280
00:13:10,025 --> 00:13:12,108
to all of her base numbers?

281
00:13:12,192 --> 00:13:13,858
With her level capped right now,

282
00:13:13,942 --> 00:13:16,275
this couldn't have
happened at a better time.

283
00:13:16,358 --> 00:13:18,275
[FITORIA] And I have
something for you, as well.

284
00:13:18,358 --> 00:13:20,817
No thanks. I really
don't want a cowlick.

285
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:22,025
What's a cowlick?

286
00:13:22,108 --> 00:13:24,150
No, this will suit you better.

287
00:13:24,233 --> 00:13:26,317
First, I'll heal your wounds.

288
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:31,650
[NAOFUMI, RAPHTALIA gasp]

289
00:13:31,733 --> 00:13:34,275
[FITORIA] Now, may I
see your shield, please?

290
00:13:34,358 --> 00:13:35,400
[NAOFUMI]
What for?

291
00:13:40,858 --> 00:13:42,692
[gasps]

292
00:13:42,775 --> 00:13:44,817
[NAOFUMI]
Force unlocked?

293
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:47,942
My level's not high enough
yet to use many of them,

294
00:13:48,025 --> 00:13:49,400
but it looks like
she gave me access

295
00:13:49,483 --> 00:13:51,858
to the entire Filolial Series.

296
00:13:51,942 --> 00:13:54,900
Bet they'll come in handy
once I can use them.

297
00:13:54,983 --> 00:13:56,608
Well, I guess I
should thank you.

298
00:13:56,692 --> 00:13:58,108
[FITORIA]
You're quite welcome.

299
00:13:58,192 --> 00:13:59,650
Now if you don't mind,

300
00:13:59,733 --> 00:14:02,150
there's something I'd like to
discuss with you privately.

301
00:14:02,233 --> 00:14:03,900
Well, that doesn't
sound ominous.

302
00:14:03,983 --> 00:14:05,983
[MELTY]
Excuse me...

303
00:14:06,067 --> 00:14:08,983
When you said...
you were testing Filo...

304
00:14:09,067 --> 00:14:11,025
Was that the reason
you took me hostage

305
00:14:11,108 --> 00:14:13,483
and stopped Naofumi
from rescuing me?

306
00:14:13,567 --> 00:14:14,692
Yes.

307
00:14:14,775 --> 00:14:17,317
And I feel terrible
for doing that to you.

308
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:19,442
Is there anything
at all you desire?

309
00:14:19,525 --> 00:14:22,108
[gasps] Well, I guess if...

310
00:14:22,192 --> 00:14:24,275
Maybe...Could I...?

311
00:14:24,358 --> 00:14:25,400
[FITORIA]
Hm?

312
00:14:35,275 --> 00:14:39,317
This is amazing! [laughs]

313
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:42,650
[gasps] It's all I ever wanted!

314
00:14:42,733 --> 00:14:45,025
[NAOFUMI] She could've asked for
anything and she wanted a ride?

315
00:14:45,108 --> 00:14:49,692
Ugh. I hope I'll get to
be gigantic like that!

316
00:14:49,775 --> 00:14:51,900
I wonder how many cowlicks
you'll have on your head

317
00:14:51,983 --> 00:14:53,192
when that happens.

318
00:14:53,275 --> 00:14:54,942
No!

319
00:14:55,025 --> 00:14:57,900
[NAOFUMI, RAPHTALIA laugh]

320
00:14:58,942 --> 00:15:02,400
[MELTY sighs]
That was so much fun!

321
00:15:02,483 --> 00:15:05,108
I realize your day
has only just begun,

322
00:15:05,192 --> 00:15:07,692
but why don't you rest a while
longer before you leave?

323
00:15:07,775 --> 00:15:10,608
Huh? Shouldn't we...

324
00:15:10,692 --> 00:15:12,692
[NAOFUMI]
Hm? I guess so.

325
00:15:12,775 --> 00:15:15,358
If Fitoria's offering,
we might as well accept.

326
00:15:15,442 --> 00:15:16,608
Really?!

327
00:15:16,692 --> 00:15:18,358
Besides, we're celebrating.

328
00:15:18,442 --> 00:15:20,692
Allow us to show you
a little hospitality.

329
00:15:20,775 --> 00:15:23,525
[filolials squawking]

330
00:15:23,608 --> 00:15:25,108
Huh?

331
00:15:25,192 --> 00:15:27,192
Wait a second. Are you trying to
throw a "new queen" party for me

332
00:15:27,275 --> 00:15:28,567
on top of everything?

333
00:15:28,650 --> 00:15:31,067
--[filolial squawks]
--Stop making decisions for me!

334
00:15:31,150 --> 00:15:33,317
Congratulations, Filo.

335
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,858
Huh? [gasps]

336
00:15:34,942 --> 00:15:36,275
[giggles]

337
00:15:36,358 --> 00:15:38,400
Huh? [gasps]

338
00:15:38,483 --> 00:15:40,483
Do I have to do this, too?

339
00:15:40,567 --> 00:15:43,150
[filolial squawks]

340
00:15:43,233 --> 00:15:43,983
Huh?

341
00:15:44,067 --> 00:15:47,400
[MELTY, RAPHTALIA scream]

342
00:15:47,483 --> 00:15:48,983
[NAOFUMI gasps]

343
00:16:17,817 --> 00:16:24,192
[FILO snoring]

344
00:16:28,442 --> 00:16:31,650
[footsteps]

345
00:16:33,067 --> 00:16:35,692
This a good time
for our private chat?

346
00:16:35,775 --> 00:16:38,483
Did you ever really try to
make up with the other heroes?

347
00:16:38,567 --> 00:16:40,358
Not this again...

348
00:16:40,442 --> 00:16:43,067
Did you make any effort
to clear your name?

349
00:16:44,733 --> 00:16:46,192
No, I didn't.

350
00:16:57,858 --> 00:16:59,692
What's the use?

351
00:16:59,775 --> 00:17:01,150
They wouldn't listen.
They've already made up

352
00:17:01,233 --> 00:17:02,858
their minds about me.

353
00:17:04,983 --> 00:17:06,858
If you don't tell them
they're wrong about you,

354
00:17:06,942 --> 00:17:09,192
they'll take it as an
admission of your guilt.

355
00:17:09,275 --> 00:17:11,108
[NAOFUMI]
Maybe you're right.

356
00:17:11,192 --> 00:17:12,567
[FITORIA]
When I take you back,

357
00:17:12,650 --> 00:17:15,192
I'm going to leave you near
one of the other heroes.

358
00:17:15,275 --> 00:17:17,775
I hope you'll take the
opportunity to talk to him.

359
00:17:17,858 --> 00:17:19,692
[NAOFUMI]
You're not coming with us, then?

360
00:17:19,775 --> 00:17:22,650
[FITORIA] I won't involve
myself any further.

361
00:17:22,733 --> 00:17:26,317
Not until you can show me
you four are worthy of it.

362
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,733
[NAOFUMI]
Seriously?

363
00:17:27,817 --> 00:17:31,150
So we're supposed to
suddenly be best friends.

364
00:17:31,233 --> 00:17:33,983
Okay, I'll try my best.

365
00:17:34,067 --> 00:17:35,817
Was that all you wanted?

366
00:17:35,900 --> 00:17:36,942
[FITORIA]
Not quite.

367
00:17:37,025 --> 00:17:38,067
You need to understand that

368
00:17:38,150 --> 00:17:40,317
if even one Cardinal
Hero is missing,

369
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:43,442
fighting off a Wave
becomes almost impossible.

370
00:17:43,525 --> 00:17:46,025
In that case, it would
be better to kill you all

371
00:17:46,108 --> 00:17:49,233
to make room for a new group
of heroes to be summoned.

372
00:17:49,317 --> 00:17:50,983
So if I really can't
figure out a way

373
00:17:51,067 --> 00:17:53,025
to make things work
with the other three,

374
00:17:53,108 --> 00:17:56,025
you meant it when you said
you'd kill all four of us?

375
00:18:02,650 --> 00:18:03,942
I can't say how many Waves

376
00:18:04,025 --> 00:18:05,900
will have passed
when it happens,

377
00:18:05,983 --> 00:18:07,775
but a time is coming when
the world will demand

378
00:18:07,858 --> 00:18:09,733
great sacrifices from all of us.

379
00:18:09,817 --> 00:18:12,900
What kind of sacrifices
are you talking about?

380
00:18:12,983 --> 00:18:14,400
[FITORIA]
There will be a battle in which

381
00:18:14,483 --> 00:18:17,942
the heroes will have to choose
what they're fighting for.

382
00:18:18,025 --> 00:18:20,317
That's the moment I'm dreading.

383
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:22,317
[NAOFUMI]
I don't get it.

384
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:24,108
[FITORIA]
Are you fighting for the world,

385
00:18:24,192 --> 00:18:26,608
or for the people
who inhabit it?

386
00:18:26,692 --> 00:18:28,400
If you choose to
fight for the world,

387
00:18:28,483 --> 00:18:30,567
many will lose their lives.

388
00:18:31,692 --> 00:18:35,650
[FITORIA] However, it will
allow you to fulfill your duty.

389
00:18:35,733 --> 00:18:39,442
And what happens if we decide
to fight for the people?

390
00:18:39,525 --> 00:18:41,608
That'll be a thorny path.

391
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:45,692
[NAOFUMI] How do you
know so much about this?

392
00:18:45,775 --> 00:18:49,108
There are too many things
that I've already forgotten.

393
00:18:49,192 --> 00:18:51,650
And yet... I do recall...

394
00:18:51,733 --> 00:18:53,650
Saving the world
and saving its people

395
00:18:53,733 --> 00:18:55,483
are not the same thing.

396
00:18:55,567 --> 00:18:57,900
The heroes that came before
you have always hoped

397
00:18:57,983 --> 00:19:00,358
that their successors would
fight for the latter.

398
00:19:00,442 --> 00:19:02,983
I don't quite understand,
but I guess it makes sense

399
00:19:03,067 --> 00:19:04,983
coming from
"heroes of the people."

400
00:19:05,067 --> 00:19:07,150
You aren't ready to
make that choice.

401
00:19:07,233 --> 00:19:09,025
It comes with many hurdles.

402
00:19:09,108 --> 00:19:11,442
And you can't conquer
them by yourself.

403
00:19:13,567 --> 00:19:16,692
[NAOFUMI] Hey...
Why come to me with this?

404
00:19:16,775 --> 00:19:17,942
Wouldn't it be easier to

405
00:19:18,025 --> 00:19:20,150
convince one of the
others to forgive me?

406
00:19:23,900 --> 00:19:25,817
I suppose it's
because I consider you

407
00:19:25,900 --> 00:19:28,400
to be a hero of higher
worth than all the others.

408
00:19:28,483 --> 00:19:29,567
Why is that?

409
00:19:29,650 --> 00:19:31,150
You raised Filo.

410
00:19:31,233 --> 00:19:33,692
Anyone who could take care
of a future filolial queen

411
00:19:33,775 --> 00:19:35,817
can't be all bad.

412
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:37,650
I'm not so sure about that.

413
00:19:37,733 --> 00:19:40,525
Whatever you say, Shield Hero.

414
00:19:40,608 --> 00:19:41,733
In any case,

415
00:19:41,817 --> 00:19:43,275
I do believe you're
up to the challenge of

416
00:19:43,358 --> 00:19:45,442
convincing the others
to work with you,

417
00:19:45,525 --> 00:19:47,692
even if you are a bad guy.

418
00:19:47,775 --> 00:19:51,067
And if not, the four
of you are far too weak.

419
00:19:51,150 --> 00:19:52,942
Even if I'm not
the one to do it,

420
00:19:53,025 --> 00:19:55,900
you're all going to die,
sooner rather than later.

421
00:19:55,983 --> 00:19:57,483
Wait a minute.
Are the upcoming battles

422
00:19:57,567 --> 00:19:59,692
really going to be that rough?

423
00:19:59,775 --> 00:20:01,608
Guess I'll just have to
get used to the Rage Shield,

424
00:20:01,692 --> 00:20:04,358
because I'm probably going
to need it more than ever.

425
00:20:04,442 --> 00:20:05,650
I'd advise against that,

426
00:20:05,733 --> 00:20:08,067
but if you truly
think it necessary...

427
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:14,317
What are you doing?

428
00:20:17,858 --> 00:20:20,817
That will slow down the
Rage Shield's corrosion.

429
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:24,233
But it won't stop it completely,
so you should still be careful.

430
00:20:24,317 --> 00:20:26,567
Use it as little as possible.

431
00:20:26,650 --> 00:20:29,233
After all that talk
about killing me?

432
00:20:29,317 --> 00:20:31,025
You're a nice person, Fitoria.

433
00:20:31,108 --> 00:20:32,192
Thank you.

434
00:20:32,275 --> 00:20:33,317
[gasps]

435
00:20:34,358 --> 00:20:37,317
You are a nice person, Fitoria.

436
00:20:41,983 --> 00:20:44,983
Uh--well, I guess since you're
doing so much to help me out,

437
00:20:45,067 --> 00:20:46,608
I kinda have to give it a shot.

438
00:20:46,692 --> 00:20:48,358
But you shouldn't
get your hopes up.

439
00:20:48,442 --> 00:20:50,650
--[rustling]
--[gasps]

440
00:20:50,733 --> 00:20:52,942
Uh, could you please get off?

441
00:20:54,317 --> 00:20:57,775
[FITORIA] Please, just for
a moment, Shield Hero.

442
00:20:59,233 --> 00:21:02,275
Hey, uh, I know that you
were raised by a hero.

443
00:21:02,358 --> 00:21:04,025
Was it the Shield Hero?

444
00:21:04,108 --> 00:21:05,525
I don't remember.

445
00:21:05,608 --> 00:21:08,150
The memory of a
filolial is short.

446
00:21:10,817 --> 00:21:11,900
Gotcha.

447
00:21:13,567 --> 00:21:14,692
[gasps]

448
00:21:16,942 --> 00:21:19,983
[FITORIA] But I do remember
that gentle touch.

449
00:23:03,317 --> 00:23:04,858
This is the place.

450
00:23:10,692 --> 00:23:12,942
[REN] The Four Cardinal
Weapons are here.

451
00:23:13,025 --> 00:23:15,692
[ITSUKI]
Yeah. We finally found them.

452
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:20,608
[gasps]

453
00:23:20,692 --> 00:23:22,358
[clattering]

454
00:23:22,442 --> 00:23:23,692
[thud]

455
00:23:23,775 --> 00:23:25,900
[REN]
Hey, what's going on here?

456
00:23:25,983 --> 00:23:26,983
It's empty!

457
00:23:27,067 --> 00:23:29,108
[COMPANIONS gasp]

458
00:23:30,358 --> 00:23:31,567
It can't be.

459
00:23:31,650 --> 00:23:33,400
Everyone, run! We've gotta--!

